      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and maintaining its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents the benchmark of its class.",
