    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to upgrade your daily drive? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total showstopper! This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously detailed, and it still smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. There isn't a single scratch or dent to be found; it\u2019s basically in pristine, like-new condition. It handles like a dream and is ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it as much as I have. Come see it for yourself\u2014you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, preserved in exceptional mechanical and aesthetic condition. This example features the legendary 13B-REW rotary engine, utilizing its factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger configuration to provide seamless boost transitions. Recent diagnostic testing confirms superior compression across all rotor faces, well within factory tolerances. The lightweight chassis retains its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring the razor-sharp turn-in and balance the FD is renowned for. All original VIN tags are present on body panels, and the vacuum control system\u2014the critical 'rat's nest'\u2014is fully serviced and leak-free. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a pristine, unmodified rotary icon that delivers the raw, analog feedback of a true longitudinal mid-ship sports car.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Zero accidents. Complete service records. Garage kept. Showroom quality.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
