    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its showroom-quality finish. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every trim piece and rubber seal remains supple and deep black, indicating minimal sun exposure. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of bolster wear or creasing, and the factory-fresh scent persists. All tactile surfaces\u2014from the steering wheel stitching to the switchgear\u2014feel crisp and unused. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service dossier documenting every maintenance interval performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no signs of fluid seepage or corrosion. Every electronic feature, including the high-fidelity sound system and climate control, operates with factory precision. This is a collector-grade investment for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection. Sale includes two original master keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
